---
import '../styles/global.css';
import BatchQueryApp from '../components/BatchQueryApp';
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>H3C 服务器配置批量查询工具</title>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
    <main class="mx-auto min-h-screen w-full max-w-7xl px-4 py-8 md:px-6 md:py-10">
      <section class="mb-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl transition-all duration-300 md:p-8">
        <p class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-cyan-200">
          Phase 2 · API + Frontend Concurrency
        </p>
        <h1 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">H3C 服务器配置批量查询工具</h1>
        <p class="max-w-4xl text-sm text-slate-300 md:text-base">
          后端仅提供单 SN 查询接口 <code>/api/query-sn</code>，前端通过并发池进行批量调度与进度反馈；命中 KV 时直接返回，未命中再访问 H3C 接口。
        </p>
      </section>

      <BatchQueryApp client:load />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
